---
title: Savoury Braised Chickpeas with Feta and Lemon-Garlic Toum
description: Protein-packed chickpeas get a flavour boost from warm Indian-style spices in this hearty and fragrant stew. You'll want to scoop up every last bite of this veggie-filled wonder!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pois-chiches-braises-3152f933.jpg
